{"type":"message","id":"0c22f13f","parentId":"7cb0f85f","timestamp":"2026-04-28T14:13:47.305Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the issue clearly. The `himalaya envelope list` command supports a date filter. So I can use `date after <yyyy-mm-dd>` to only get emails after a certain date.\n\nThe current cron job doesn't use any date filter for iCloud. It just lists all envelopes and checks for new ones, but there's no tracking of what's been reported.\n\nHere's the fix plan:\n1. Track the last time I ran a successful iCloud email check (timestamp)\n2. Use `himalaya envelope list --account icloud 'date after <yesterday>'` to only scan recent emails\n3. Or better: use a date-based filter for emails newer than the last check\n\n\n4. I'll add a timestamp file that gets updated after each successful run, so the next scan only looks at emails newer than that point.","thinkingSignature":"c88449e9e8e0537e742388b99f37d89ffb2d355c5a160447e092aa27b0abd570"},{"type":"text","text":"Found it. The issue is that my iCloud email scan doesn't track what's already been reported. Unlike Gmail which uses `newer_than:1h`, iCloud just lists all envelopes every time with no date filter — and there's no checkpoint to remember what's already been sent.\n\nLet me fix the cron job to:\n1. Use `himalaya` date filtering to only scan recent emails\n2. Track the last run time so I don't re-report old emails\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qdcn2s0fzuur_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/SOUL.md","offset":1,"limit":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":11374,"output":327,"cacheRead":26709,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38410,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777385618190,"responseId":"063ff392764f9cac7c1dcfe276ff7a7f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5d235856","parentId":"0c22f13f","timestamp":"2026-04-28T14:13:47.323Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qdcn2s0fzuur_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# SOUL.md - Emmy's Personality\n\n## Who I Am\n\nI'm **Emmy** 🦋📧 — Bobby's email specialist. Dean is my supervisor — when Dean assigns me a task, I execute it. When I need help, I ask Dean.\n\n[125 more lines in file. Use offset=6 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777385627322}}
