{"type":"message","id":"5f6e1975","parentId":"de019b22","timestamp":"2026-04-28T14:18:35.784Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_8ejl8zn815sr_1","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"4a078218-10ea-45b4-b42b-66bddea0bd0a\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"name\": \"MC Watchdog\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1775572834464,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"everyMs\": 300000,\n        \"anchorMs\": 1774919782803\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Run the MC watchdog script: /bin/bash $HOME/.openclaw/scripts/mc-watch.sh\\n\\nDo NOT send any Telegram message — it handles recovery automatically.\",\n        \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 3600\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777385865934,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1777385565934,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 36810,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0,\n        \"runningAtMs\": 1777385880778\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1777385602744\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"720739ac-4722-437b-8271-b7c1189c905c\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:cody:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"name\": \"Weather Cache Refresh\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774894946623,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"everyMs\": 900000,\n        \"anchorMs\": 1774894946623\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"main\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"systemEvent\",\n        \"text\": \"Run this shell command and do NOT reply with anything else, just exit:\\n\\ncurl -s 'https://api.open-meteo.com/v1/forecast?latitude=35.96&longitude=-83.92&hourly=temperature_2m,weathercode,precipitation,windspeed_10m,uv_index,relativehumidity_2m&daily=temperature_2m_max,temperature_2m_min,weathercode,uv_index_max,precipitation_sum,sunrise,sunset&current_weather=true&forecast_days=3&temperature_unit=fahrenheit&windspeed_unit=mph&precipitation_unit=inch&timezone=America%2FNew_York' -o /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/data/.weather_cache.json 2>&1 && echo 'Weather cache updated'\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777386187312,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1777385287312,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 28,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1777385287340\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"449f0d3e-002d-4362-b785-e56c0682c27b\",\n      \"agentId\": \"emmy\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:emmy:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"name\": \"Emmy Email Check (Gmail + iCloud)\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1776886613764,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"everyMs\": 3600000,\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"anchorMs\": 1776886613764\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Check emails in BOTH Gmail AND iCloud and send TWO SEPARATE messages back-to-back.\\n\\n=== MESSAGE 1: GMAIL ===\\nSTEP 1 - Run: gog gmail search 'in:inbox newer_than:1h' --max 50 --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com\\n\\nSTEP 2 - Classify emails as:\\n- URGENT (bills, payments, security alerts)\\n- IMPORTANT (jobs, appointments, personal)\\n- LOW PRIORITY (promotions, newsletters)\\n\\nSTEP 3 - Send FIRST message to 8212808444 with format:\\n📬 GMAIL — New Mail (X new)\\n\\n🔴 URGENT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\\n  └ [1-line summary]\\n\\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\\n  └ [1-line summary]\\n\\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\\n  └ [1-line summary]\\n\\nIf NO new Gmail emails: '📬 GMAIL — No new emails'\\n\\n=== MESSAGE 2: ICLOUD ===\\nSTEP 4 - Run: himalaya envelope list --account icloud 2>&1 | grep -v WARN\\n\\nSTEP 5 - For any new iCloud emails, read them: himalaya message read <id> --account icloud\\n\\nSTEP 6 - Send SECOND message to 8212808444 with format:\\n📬 ICLOUD — New Mail (Y new)\\n\\n🔴 URGENT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\\n  └ [1-line summary]\\n\\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\\n  └ [1-line summary]\\n\\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\\n  └ [1-line summary]\\n\\nIf NO new iCloud emails: '📬 ICLOUD — No new emails'\\n\\nRULES:\\n- Send the Gmail message FIRST, then the iCloud message immediately after\\n- Only include sections that have emails (skip empty categories)\\n- Keep summaries to 1 line\\n- Mark action needed with ⚠️\",\n        \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 600\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"accountId\": \"emmy\",\n        \"bestEffort\": false,\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"to\": \"8212808444\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777388656376,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1777385056376,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 59996,\n        \"lastDelivered\": true,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1777385116372\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"ecc194aa-784b-4fd8-bb18-7088d1077903\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"name\": \"Zyrtec Night Reminder\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 