{"type":"message","id":"af9a5149","parentId":"62339b1a","timestamp":"2026-04-28T14:19:34.477Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me update the cron job with the fixed message that tracks the last seen iCloud email ID.","thinkingSignature":"f129b9d1e865272218ecbf0f81b14236ac484d5dacd4d9f2f9a517ba71485c4c"},{"type":"text","text":"Now let me update the cron job with proper iCloud deduplication:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0efxba6ncco0_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"update","jobId":"449f0d3e-002d-4362-b785-e56c0682c27b","patch":{"payload":{"message":"Check emails in BOTH Gmail AND iCloud and send TWO SEPARATE messages back-to-back.\n\n=== MESSAGE 1: GMAIL ===\nSTEP 1 - Run: gog gmail search 'in:inbox newer_than:1h' --max 50 --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com\n\nSTEP 2 - Classify emails as:\n- URGENT (bills, payments, security alerts)\n- IMPORTANT (jobs, appointments, personal)\n- LOW PRIORITY (promotions, newsletters)\n\nSTEP 3 - Send FIRST message to 8212808444 with format:\n📬 GMAIL — New Mail (X new)\n\n🔴 URGENT:\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\n  └ [1-line summary]\n\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\n  └ [1-line summary]\n\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\n  └ [1-line summary]\n\nIf NO new Gmail emails: '📬 GMAIL — No new emails'\n\n=== MESSAGE 2: ICLOUD (with deduplication) ===\nSTEP 4 - Read last seen ID: cat ~/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_icloud_id.txt 2>/dev/null || echo \"0\"\n\nSTEP 5 - List iCloud emails (newest first): himalaya envelope list --account icloud 'order by date desc' 2>&1 | grep -v WARN\n\nSTEP 6 - For each email where ID > last_seen_ID:\n  - Read it: himalaya message read <id> --account icloud\n  - Note its content for reporting\n\nSTEP 7 - Send SECOND message to 8212808444 with format:\n📬 ICLOUD — New Mail (Y new)\n\n🔴 URGENT:\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\n  └ [1-line summary]\n\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\n  └ [1-line summary]\n\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\n  └ [1-line summary]\n\nIf NO new iCloud emails: '📬 ICLOUD — No new emails'\n\nSTEP 8 - After sending, update checkpoint: echo <highest_new_id> > ~/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_icloud_id.txt\n\nRULES:\n- Send the Gmail message FIRST, then the iCloud message immediately after\n- Only include sections that have emails (skip empty categories)\n- Keep summaries to 1 line\n- Mark action needed with ⚠️\n- ICLOUD: Only report emails with ID strictly greater than the saved last_icloud_id"}}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":15477,"output":702,"cacheRead":26709,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42888,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777385960566,"responseId":"063ff4e8fd5970900bd3e107d3cbe291"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e444502b","parentId":"af9a5149","timestamp":"2026-04-28T14:19:34.508Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_0efxba6ncco0_1","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"449f0d3e-002d-4362-b785-e56c0682c27b\",\n  \"agentId\": \"emmy\",\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:emmy:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n  \"name\": \"Emmy Email Check (Gmail + iCloud)\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1776886613764,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"everyMs\": 3600000,\n    \"kind\": \"every\",\n    \"anchorMs\": 1776886613764\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"Check emails in BOTH Gmail AND iCloud and send TWO SEPARATE messages back-to-back.\\n\\n=== MESSAGE 1: GMAIL ===\\nSTEP 1 - Run: gog gmail search 'in:inbox newer_than:1h' --max 50 --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com\\n\\nSTEP 2 - Classify emails as:\\n- URGENT (bills, payments, security alerts)\\n- IMPORTANT (jobs, appointments, personal)\\n- LOW PRIORITY (promotions, newsletters)\\n\\nSTEP 3 - Send FIRST message to 8212808444 with format:\\n📬 GMAIL — New Mail (X new)\\n\\n🔴 URGENT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\\n  └ [1-line summary]\\n\\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\\n  └ [1-line summary]\\n\\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\\n  └ [1-line summary]\\n\\nIf NO new Gmail emails: '📬 GMAIL — No new emails'\\n\\n=== MESSAGE 2: ICLOUD (with deduplication) ===\\nSTEP 4 - Read last seen ID: cat ~/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_icloud_id.txt 2>/dev/null || echo \\\"0\\\"\\n\\nSTEP 5 - List iCloud emails (newest first): himalaya envelope list --account icloud 'order by date desc' 2>&1 | grep -v WARN\\n\\nSTEP 6 - For each email where ID > last_seen_ID:\\n  - Read it: himalaya message read <id> --account icloud\\n  - Note its content for reporting\\n\\nSTEP 7 - Send SECOND message to 8212808444 with format:\\n📬 ICLOUD — New Mail (Y new)\\n\\n🔴 URGENT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\\n  └ [1-line summary]\\n\\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\\n  └ [1-line summary]\\n\\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\\n  └ [1-line summary]\\n\\nIf NO new iCloud emails: '📬 ICLOUD — No new emails'\\n\\nSTEP 8 - After sending, update checkpoint: echo <highest_new_id> > ~/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_icloud_id.txt\\n\\nRULES:\\n- Send the Gmail message FIRST, then the iCloud message immediately after\\n- Only include sections that have emails (skip empty categories)\\n- Keep summaries to 1 line\\n- Mark action needed with ⚠️\\n- ICLOUD: Only report emails with ID strictly greater than the saved last_icloud_id\",\n    \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\",\n    \"timeoutSeconds\": 600\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"accountId\": \"emmy\",\n    \"bestEffort\": false,\n    \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"to\": \"8212808444\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777388656376,\n    \"lastRunAtMs\": 1777385056376,\n    \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n    \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n    \"lastDurationMs\": 59996,\n    \"lastDelivered\": true,\n    \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n    \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n    \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n  },\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1777385974497\n}"}],"details":{"id":"449f0d3e-002d-4362-b785-e56c0682c27b","agentId":"emmy","sessionKey":"agent:emmy:telegram:direct:8212808444","name":"Emmy Email Check (Gmail + iCloud)","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1776886613764,"schedule":{"everyMs":3600000,"kind":"every","anchorMs":1776886613764},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"Check emails in BOTH Gmail AND iCloud and send TWO SEPARATE messages back-to-back.\n\n=== MESSAGE 1: GMAIL ===\nSTEP 1 - Run: gog gmail search 'in:inbox newer_than:1h' --max 50 --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com\n\nSTEP 2 - Classify emails as:\n- URGENT (bills, payments, security alerts)\n- IMPORTANT (jobs, appointments, personal)\n- LOW PRIORITY (promotions, newsletters)\n\nSTEP 3 - Send FIRST message to 8212808444 with format:\n📬 GMAIL — New Mail (X new)\n\n🔴 URGENT:\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\n  └ [1-line summary]\n\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\n  └ [1-line summary]\n\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\n  └ [1-line summary]\n\nIf NO new Gmail emails: '📬 GMAIL — No new emails'\n\n=== MESSAGE 2: ICLOUD (with deduplication) ===\nSTEP 4 - Read last seen ID: cat ~/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_icloud_id.txt 2>/dev/null || echo \"0\"\n\nSTEP 5 - List iCloud emails (newest first): himalaya envelope list --account icloud 'order by date desc' 2>&1 | grep -v WARN\n\nSTEP 6 - For each email where ID > last_seen_ID:\n  - Read it: himalaya message read <id> --account icloud\n  - Note its content for reporting\n\nSTEP 7 - Send SECOND message to 8212808444 with format:\n📬 ICLOUD — New Mail (Y new)\n\n🔴 URGENT:\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\n  └ [1-line summary]\n\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\n  └ [1-line summary]\n\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\n  └ [1-line summary]\n\nIf NO new iCloud emails: '📬 ICLOUD — No new emails'\n\nSTEP 8 - After sending, update checkpoint: echo <highest_new_id> > ~/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_icloud_id.txt\n\nRULES:\n- Send the Gmail message FIRST, then the iCloud message immediately after\n- Only include sections that have emails (skip empty categories)\n- Keep summaries to 1 line\n- Mark action needed with ⚠️\n- ICLOUD: Only report emails with ID strictly greater than the saved last_icloud_id","model":"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7","timeoutSeconds":600},"delivery":{"accountId":"emmy","bestEffort":false,"channel":"telegram","mode":"announce","to":"8212808444"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1777388656376,"lastRunAtMs":1777385056376,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":59996,"lastDelivered":true,"lastDeliveryStatus":"delivered","consecutiveErrors":0,"consecutiveSkipped":0},"updatedAtMs":1777385974497},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777385974508}}
{"type":"message","id":"433c3197","parentId":"e444502b","timestamp":"2026-04-28T14:19:43.826Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The cron job is updated. Now let me verify the checkpoint file is correctly set to 10 (the most recent email ID), so the next run won't re-report the RC Leasing emails.","thinkingSignature":"92550e9a45d081bcfcdb151ef1fcd2e783249657992ecc95c7acd418314bb84a"},{"type":"text","text":"Done. Here's what was wrong and what I fixed:\n\n**The problem:** The iCloud check ran `himalaya envelope list --account icloud` with **no filter at all** — every time it fired, it listed all iCloud emails from scratch. There was no checkpoint to remember what you'd already seen.\n\n**The fix:**\n1. Set a checkpoint file at `~/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_icloud_id.txt` with the most recent iCloud email ID (10)\n2. Updated the cron job to:\n   - Read that checkpoint before scanning\n   - Only report emails with ID **newer than** (higher than) the saved ID\n   - Update the checkpoint to the highest new ID after each successful run\n\nSo that RC Leasing email (ID 10) will NOT be reported again — it's now the baseline. Only emails with IDs 11, 12, etc. will show up as \"new.\" 🎯"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":17140,"output":238,"cacheRead":26709,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44087,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777385974509,"responseId":"063ff4f67bc8a44f09e33fbda54b96d3"}}
